Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:49.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:54.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:24.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:30.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:35.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:44.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:50.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:56.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:01.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've decided to head to Elbaf!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What?! Please don't go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I was just kidding. I know how you guys feel."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"So you're coming back, Usopp?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Of course I am, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you guys must like me so much!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that idiot doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everyone Finally Has A Bounty!\NA Pirate Group Worth Over 600 Million!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokozuna! I need lumber! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit, ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit, ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, those two are extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you'd expect from Tom's Workers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're barely keeping up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It boggles the mind that they\Ncould work at such a crazy pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there isn't even the\Nslightest fault in their work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna get anywhere by\Njust sitting here and admiring them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show them what us\NDock #1 workers are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokozuna! Guys! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered you used to collect junk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and built a bunch of weird\Nbattleships on this scrap heap island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't like me building weapons, did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. On top of that, they were\Nused to frame Tom-san as a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by looking at this, I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that your experience building those\Nbattleships wasn't a waste at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Is that sarcasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show Tom-san that\Nthe Moron-ky from back then has...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this ship, going to the New\NWorld is no longer a pipe dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:04:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even before Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can resolutely stand proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought those two would\Nwork together to build a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...! What the hell are you doing\Ninstead of helping me with work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you keep making\Nunstable stuff like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's none of\Nyour business, Stupid-berg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what's with him?!\NYou should just kick out an idiot like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't say that. He's a fellow ship builder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His shipbuilding skills are already almost\Non par with the craftsmen on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...though what he makes is shaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just always honest, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two will definitely become\Nworld-class shipbuilding engineers someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be nice to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way things are going,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it looks like we'll be able to\Nfinish it sooner than we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg, let me tell you one thing.\NThis isn't just another pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You've put your heart into--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats went head-on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,against not only Navy Headquarters,\Nbut the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ship they'll be traveling on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, the mayor of Water Seven,\Ntook part in building it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that becomes known, you could be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do understand that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, did you forget what Tom-san said?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, there's no such thing\Nas blueprints for a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the sailors who board a ship put up\Na skull flag, then it's a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they put up a seagull flag,\Nthen it's a Navy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you wanna build,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a man should be resolutely\Nproud of the ship he built!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Galley-La has been building ships\Nbased on that creed all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm giving you a hand\Ntowards achieving your dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I feel that... I'm not in my right mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I asked you to\Ngive me a hand, Stupid-berg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You abandoned your real name
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your body, too, is like that\Nof a completely different man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't changed at all.\NYou're just the way you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream... Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Tom-san back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Sea train!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna build ships anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't love ships that hurt\Nthe people I really care about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're my goal after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to come back\Nand teach me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...build a dream ship someday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship that resolutely and proudly traverses
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even uncharted waves at edges of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream ship like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bites... My body... is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if I'll die like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see no one on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An abandoned ship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scrap wood... Scrap iron...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place makes me... feel quite at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something\Nabout my disabled body first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... anyway, what's up with\Nthat funny looking body of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Since my whole\Nbody became of no use,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rebuilt my body using iron\Nscraps and escaped death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never change, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet face to face,\Nwe yell at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still won't forgive you... and you\Nmay feel the same about me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky... I'm... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...glad that... you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with "I'm glad that you're alive"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I'm alive, he ended up\Nhelping me achieve my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite an idiot, too, Iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Whoa, Luffy! What a coincidence\Nto see you in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just taking a stroll...\Nbut, well, this must just be fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do? I'll come\Nback and rejoin the gang!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is pattern 53.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not being able to use it\Nunless they find me is a flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I should take\Nsome initiative myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! That's what I'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why are they all looking so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the Straw Hats\Nreally have become edgy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lost their cohesiveness without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, for everyone's sake, I'll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pattern 34!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah-choo! Ah-choo!\NGeez, that night breeze is cold!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd sneeze loudly so that they'd hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, they're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the crucial moment. I definitely\Nhave to act like this is a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, is that you over there, Usopp?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, I just happened to be passing by."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You shouldn't stay outside, you'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come inside and have something warm."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, yeah? Well, I know\Nexactly how you guys feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you need me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let bygones be bygones!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're going to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new ship is coming\Ntogether quickly, and I haven't yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to somehow rejoin the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now that it's come to this,\NI'll come up with more patterns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! I brought some food and drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you Galley-La guys, too! Take a little break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought you cold cola, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We chilled them good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaay! I was pretty hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you brought some\Nof this stuff, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san! Franky!\NGo ahead and take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have been working\Nwithout eating or drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can keep on going like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we can take a break later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... then I'll take you up on that offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not a bad idea for me\Nto replenish cola and power up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Replenishment completed! Super... Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah, he is!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, what're you going to do\Nonce the ship is completed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you hand the ship over to the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you going to be satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you've achieved your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like those guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I told you so many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention whatsoever\Nof leaving this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm gonna go back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokozuna, you sit back and relax for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie, it's you guys' turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we're so exhausted that we\Ncan't even manage a late-night snack...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are the very\Ndefinition of inexhaustible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a party once the ship is completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a short time, but I had fun with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally met someone worthy\Nof entrusting with my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I promised, I'm gonna build an amazing ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg! Why don't you take it\Neasy and get some sleep, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm feeling super energetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you watching this, Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were called a legendary shipwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your skills and spirit were\Npassed down to your disciples splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A log has been stored!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Log Pose is pointing to the next island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, all we need now is the ship!\NI'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He told us not to come until it's\Ndone because he wants to surprise us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys know where\Nfollowing that log will take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It somehow looks like it's\Npointing a little downwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is. The next island\Nis a paradise on the seabed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! F-F-Fishman Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's wrong, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman Island, huh?\NI have mixed feelings about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it reminds us of what\Nhappened in your village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even though they were fishmen,\Nthey were pirates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're exactly right, though you're stupid,\Nyou damn jerk! I'm impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman Island is a famous\Nplace in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful mermaids draw arcs\Nover the water and play with fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dream kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I be allowed to dream?! I'm a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do have young ones there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not easy to get to this paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm concerned about it being on the seabed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll see once we go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at the front page.\NIt's a recent newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fourteen more ships have\Ndisappeared this month."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Devil's Triangle,\Nalso known as the Florian Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't reach paradise without\Npassing through that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that sea, more than 100\Nships go missing every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after they go missing, sometimes\Nthe ships will show up with no crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and increasingly, people are seeing\Nghost ships with a dead crew on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts?! That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can meet skeletons that are alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of imagination do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I definitely don't wanna encounter them!\NI don't wanna even see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such creepy ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens in that sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who encounter trouble\Nnever come back, so I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dark sea with deep fog. So be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:19:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's a dangerous sea\Nwhere lots of disasters happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you are well\Nprepared before you set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the stories about ghost ships--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in other words, wrecked trading\Nships and pirate ships--there are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...legends of treasure ships, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find ghost ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the worry's just about getting lost,\Ndon't worry, as we'll have plenty of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure ships, huh? I wonder\Nif they have swords, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Franky asked us to bring you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dream ship has been completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They built an incredible ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's already done?!\NThat was really quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five top-notch shipwrights\Nworked on it day and night!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:19:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's head there right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys running that\Nfrantically for? You're out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, we came\Nto ask you a huge favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the wanted posters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted posters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, the bounty on\Nyour head has gotten crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all the others, too, are wanted in addition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too?! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of having me explain,\Njust take a look at these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All seven of you now have\Nbounties on your heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy, 300-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It went up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Hunter Zoro, 120-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat Burglar Nami, 16-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cotton Candy Lover Chopper,\Nthe gang's pet, 50-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil's Child Nico Robin,\N80-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot Sanji, failed to obtain\Na picture, 77-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sogeking's got a bounty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, we sympathize with you, or well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you wanna say all sorts\Nof things, but, well... please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The favor we're talking about\Nhas something to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyborg Franky, 44-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Bro's got a bounty on his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We somehow\Nwere able to get off the hook,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Bro had no such luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he stays in Water Seven,\Nhis life will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets caught again, we're not\Nstrong enough to rescue him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he probably will try to stay on this\Nisland because he's worried about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we got together and discussed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, please! You can\Ndo it by force if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take Bro out to sea.\NHe's a pirate's son to start with!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go get our new ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:22:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! So is that it, Luffy?! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:22:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky! Where are you, Franky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The King of Animals that Overlooks the Sea!\NThe Dream Ship Magnificently Completed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.11,0:23:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
